OL,5,G1900 Inside the Ambulance
OL,6,     FThe crews attend a man with an
OL,7,     Funexplained broken leg, a boy with
OL,8,     Fpneumonia and a woman with
OL,9,     Fbreathing problems. They also help
OL,10,     Fa man who has fallen under the
OL,11,     Fwheels of his own car.
OL,12,G2000 Inside the Operating Theatre
OL,13,     F3-year-old Isaac has an operation
OL,14,     Fon his tongue, Lynette has several
OL,15,     Ftoes straightened and David has
OL,16,     Fbiopsies taken from his prostate.
