OL,5,G2240 The Catherine Tate Show
OL,6,     FLook at her face, though... is she
OL,7,     Fbovvered? It's the award-winning
OL,8,     Fcomedy sketch series with the very
OL,9,     Fversatile actress. Bernie the
OL,10,     FIrish nurse is feeling a little
OL,11,     Fromantic.
OL,12,G2320 The Catherine Tate Show
OL,13,     FThe hilarious comedy sketch series
OL,14,     Fco-written and performed by the
OL,15,     Fvery versatile comedy actress.
OL,16,     FSketches this time round include
OL,17,     FMargaret the jumpy woman, plus
OL,18,     FPaul and Sam.
